    "description": "《骰出生路》是一款独立单机的类Rogue回合制牌组构建游戏，面对强大的敌人，你需要充分利用骰子卡牌管理经营自己的手牌去战胜他们。击败所有敌人，并探索游戏背后的故事。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >固定的起手牌组</h2>不同的职业会给你不同的起手牌组，职业可能附带某种特殊属性。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/dbc368f18f5826f39555aa5a5a8de4db.avif?t=1747731808\" width=550 height=296 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌握骰子就能掌握游戏</h2>骰子牌是核心，你可以通过骰子改变游戏中非红色的数值，强大的牌组需要有强大的骰子。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/8ba43be65f20f2462273ce42832b12fe.poster.avif?t=1747731808\" width=550 height=296 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/8ba43be65f20f2462273ce42832b12fe.webm?t=1747731808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/8ba43be65f20f2462273ce42832b12fe.mp4?t=1747731808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >敌人也有天赋技能</h2>敌人的天赋可能是天克你的牌组的，所以应对不同的敌人，不同的卡牌产生的效果千差万别<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/1e713b95753ee77c319ae7716713cb76.avif?t=1747731808\" width=550 height=296 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >过关奖励是丰富牌组的重要途径</h2>认真挑选你的奖励，这是走得更远的秘诀……<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2321240/extras/88ec6807f418239c50e2fb34dcb47cf3.avif?t=1747731808\" width=550 height=296 /></span>",
